packet, not as a cost, but as a person

1584
01:31:46.102 --> 01:31:48.322
I love dancing. I love making people smile.

1585
01:31:48.502 --> 01:31:51.302
I love being around people. I love seeing

1586
01:31:52.282 --> 01:31:55.882
