1602
01:32:51.982 --> 01:32:55.322
I just know that they've gone, and that loss is very real.

1603
01:32:56.302 --> 01:32:59.182
My family are different. They have been beside me my whole life.

1604
01:32:59.682 --> 01:33:02.062
They know what makes me laugh. They know when I'm frightened.

1605
01:33:02.122 --> 01:33:05.222
They know how I communicate when words are hard.

1606
01:33:06.022 --> 01:33:08.242
