01:33:18.542 --> 01:33:22.302
That knowledge has been built over a lifetime. It comes from love.

1611
01:33:22.422 --> 01:33:25.622
It comes from commitment. It comes from never giving up on me.

1612
01:33:26.182 --> 01:33:29.042
Believe me when I tell you, people have given up on

1613
