1617
01:33:41.962 --> 01:33:45.862
I may not learn the same things as everyone else, but that doesn't mean what

1618
01:33:45.982 --> 01:33:47.302
I learn doesn't matter.

1619
01:33:48.442 --> 01:33:50.462
