1627
01:34:14.162 --> 01:34:16.862
All of my sisters are talented. I love to watch them sing.

1628
01:34:17.362 --> 01:34:19.542
I cannot sing. I can barely talk.

1629
01:34:21.062 --> 01:34:22.842
I'm just going to stop the sharing now.

1630
01:34:24.802 --> 01:34:28.262
So yeah, I can't barely talk, actually. I am profoundly deaf.

1631
01:34:28.882 --> 01:34:32.192
But I can dance, and I am really good at dancing.

1632
01:34:33.162 --> 01:34:34.742
When I dance, people smile,

1633
01:34:36.842 --> 01:34:40.482
and people laugh. And when I dance, other people feel

1634
01:34:40.522 --> 01:34:42.982
happy, and being happy makes

1635
01:34:43.022 --> 01:34:46.502
