and we matter.

1653
01:35:46.602 --> 01:35:49.082
I want you to think about my family and your family.

1654
01:35:50.082 --> 01:35:53.362
They have their own dreams, and they have their own goals, their own

1655
01:35:53.402 --> 01:35:56.222
relationships, their own lives that they want to live.

1656
01:35:57.342 --> 01:36:01.122
I do not want the people I love to have to give up their futures just so that I can

1657
